BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 470 Td (ChatGPT and similar AI can help you process feelings through guided journaling prompts.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 449 Td (AI recognizes signs that you may need professional help and suggests resources.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 428 Td (Memorial creation tools help you honor your loved one's memory in meaningful ways.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 407 Td (AI-guided meditation specifically for grief helps manage overwhelming waves of emotion.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 386 Td (Connecting with others who understand your loss creates powerful healing bonds.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 365 Td (Professional telehealth therapy enhanced by AI is available without leaving home.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 344 Td (Grief is not something to overcome alone - let technology connect you with support.) Tj ET

endstream
