BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 36 608 Td (Chapter 14: Building a Daily Social Routine with AI) Tj ET
q 0.4 G 1 w 36 600 m 396 600 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 575 Td (Consistency is the key to overcoming loneliness - build social connection into every day.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 554 Td (MORNING: Voice assistant greeting, news discussion, or AI companion chat \(10 minutes\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 533 Td (MIDMORNING: Check and respond to family group messages and social media \(15 minutes\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 512 Td (LUNCH: Video call with a friend, family member, or online community member \(20 minutes\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 491 Td (AFTERNOON: Participate in one online activity, hobby group, or class \(30 minutes\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 470 Td (EVENING: Phone call, letter writing, or AI companion conversation \(15 minutes\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 449 Td (AI reminders ensure you do not skip social activities even on low-energy days.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 428 Td (Track your social interactions weekly - aim for at least 3 meaningful connections daily.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 407 Td (Balance digital connection with in-person contact whenever possible.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 386 Td (Volunteer one hour per week online to gain purpose and human appreciation.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 365 Td (Join one new group or activity per month to continually expand your social circle.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 344 Td (Remember: connection is a skill that improves with practice. Start small and build.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
